summary: An Ordinance providing for the improvement of Lane Street, from Eighteenth Avenue South to Rainer Avenue; and Sixteenth Avenue South, from Weller Street to Lane Street, all in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing the same, in accordance with Majority Petition, being File No. 33932; and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Payment by Bonds," as provided by the laws of the State of Washington and the Charter and Ordinances of the City of Seattle
